definition: strong/powerful/better/slightly more than/vigorous/violent/best in their category, e.g. see 百強|百强[bai3 qiang2]
to force/to compel/to strive/to make an effort

sentences.english: Then, from Tuesday afternoon through Thursday, the stars send intense and beautiful energy your way.
sentences.chinese: 從週二下午到週四，巨蟹宮將會釋放強勁的能量。

sentences.english: The strongest , fastest winds of a hurricane are found in the eyewall.
sentences.chinese: 最強勁最快速的風在颶風的眼壁中。

sentences.english: The taste is healthy, the vitality is abundant, then the muscle is plentiful, the body is strong.
sentences.chinese: 脾胃健，氣血盛，則肌肉豐腴，肢體強勁。

sentences.english: The strong gusts whipped up eddies of fallen leaves.
sentences.chinese: 強勁的陣風激起了落葉漩渦。

sentences.english: The robust RJ45 connectors are also shielded against electrical interference.
sentences.chinese: 強勁的RJ45連接器也屏蔽防止電波干擾。

sentences.english: The test will be whether they can continue that streak.
sentences.chinese: 但能否延續這一強勁勢頭是他們所面臨的考驗。

sentences.english: Strong cross-winds blew the aircraft off course.
sentences.chinese: 強勁的側風把飛機吹得偏離了航線。

sentences.english: Adaptation alone will not be able to accommodate unabated climate change.
sentences.chinese: 適應氣候變化本身不能緩解強勁的氣候變化。

sentences.english: 'China will continue to grow, and grow strongly, ' Ms. Gillard said.
sentences.chinese: 吉拉德說，中國經濟將繼續增長，而且會非常強勁。

sentences.english: Wang, at the Commerce Ministry, said that demand from abroad remained strong.
sentences.chinese: 商務部的王超表示外國需求依然強勁。

sentences.english: Lianyuan mining and machinery maintained a powerful momentum of development.
sentences.chinese: 漣源煤機發展勢頭強勁。

sentences.english: In the main competition, female director to show strong momentum.
sentences.chinese: 在主競賽單元，女導演表現出強勁勢頭。

sentences.english: Good strong match, worthily for union armed force first soldiers.
sentences.chinese: 好強勁的對手，不愧爲聯合軍第一戰士。

sentences.english: The newly introduced high-end server demonstrates its powerful performance.
sentences.chinese: 新進引入的高端服務器顯示了強勁的功能。

sentences.english: He said demand remains robust despite the lower subsidies.
sentences.chinese: 熊傳林說，儘管補貼下降，但需求依舊強勁。

sentences.english: Tannic when young, round and elegant if matured.
sentences.chinese: 年輕時丹寧強勁，成熟時優雅而圓潤。
